title: Grateful Dead Live at Red Rocks Amphitheatre on 1978-07-07
description:
Set One
Jack Straw ; Candyman ; Me And My Uncle > Big River ; Friend Of The Devil ; Cassidy ; Tennessee Jed ; Passenger ; Peggy-O ; The Music Never Stopped

Set Two
Cold Rain And Snow ; Beat It On Down The Line ; Scarlet Begonias > Fire On The Mountain ; Dancing In The Street > Drums > Space > Not Fade Away > Black Peter > Around And Around

Encore
U.S. Blues ; Johnny B. Goode

reviews.review_text: they have a t-shirt of this show at walmart are the dead now fashionable...lol

Red Rocks 7/7,8/78 Out effing standing Jerry screaming "Ship of Fools"7/8 is worth listening to with the wolf screaming too. if that was the only song it would be five stars however Jerry’s voice is still sweet here 7/7 the entire night and the following night are in my history book. Being there was absolutely cosmic. hey Allen RIP Peace Love Happiness &The Grateful Dead to all*****************
